      <title>津巴布韦央行积累了近一吨黄金储备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-13/zimbabwe-central-bank-accumulates-almost-a-ton-of-gold-reserves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自从颁布一项法律，迫使矿业公司使用黄金支付部分特许权使用费以来，津巴布韦央行积累了 793 公斤（25,000 盎司）的黄金储备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-13/zimbabwe-central-bank-accumulates-almost-a-ton-of-gold-reserves</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 11:12:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>研究显示，通货膨胀已使德国工资回到 2016 年水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-13/inflation-has-sent-german-pay-back-to-2016-levels-study-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近年来不断飙升的物价已将德国经通胀调整后的工资推回到2016年的水平——一项研究表明，大幅加薪的论调增强了，该研究的结果可能会让欧洲央行感到担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-13/inflation-has-sent-german-pay-back-to-2016-levels-study-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 11:06:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
